{"tid":2300294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"八區開花地盤工推跌警長 襲警罪成遭還柙","createTime":"2020-11-25T11:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T18:47:16.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"04cf8fb182f2966c7f0c95f17971504ead82ab16","tid":2300294,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:40:32.000Z","msg":"裁判官鍾明新裁決指，涉案警員作供清晰直接，沒有誇大或不合理之處，因此接納其證供。鍾官又指，自己曾細心觀看涉案呈堂片段，就涉嫌推警人士的衣著打扮與被告屋內搜出衣飾作多番對比，確認兩者為同一人，認為控方已成功舉證，裁定被告罪成。<br />\n<br />\n代表被告的大律師劉偉聰求情透露，被告於1996年從內地來港，原為會計畢業生，惟因資歷在港不獲確認，轉職於地盤工作，現與罹患第三期肺癌的母親相依為命，需照顧病母，直言若判處監禁，對母親而言必然苦上加苦。<br />\n<br />\n鍾官下令先為被告索取背景報告，案件押後至12月9日判刑，其間被告須還柙。"},{"pid":"0858c94aca777a820487ff0fc7bbd4df8f928b1b","tid":2300294,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/UJKN4CZI7NCIXCKJZYXZZSNULI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FUJKN4CZI7NCIXCKJZYXZZSNULI%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=a70a45c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FUJKN4CZI7NCIXCKJZYXZZSNULI%2F&h=d54f892c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/UJKN4CZI7NCIXCKJZYXZZSNULI/</a>"},{"pid":"92e858f9dabbfaca094c6c731a8be2ca2907d014","tid":2300294,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705d5b5e1e0fa8ebc7a33b160e470383f7c0444f","tid":2300294,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976355